UPDATING MULTIPLE FIELDS

 UPDATE emp_detail SET EmployeeName='Raghav',Gender='M' WHERE EmployeeID=7;
Query OK, 1 row affected (0.01 sec)
Rows matched: 1  Changed: 1  Warnings: 0

mysql> SELECT*FROM emp_detail;
